            <div style="font-size:0.65rem; color:#9ca3af; margin-top:0.2rem;">1,444 GDELT matches sampled — 3 false positives (Odessa only)</div>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:1rem; background:#fefce8; border-radius:6px; text-align:center;">
            <div style="font-size:1.8rem; font-weight:700; color:#d97706;">p=0.035</div>
            <div style="font-size:0.75rem; color:#6b7280;">Category test</div>
